{"tid":2032364,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"認唔認同呢幾年 丸龜統治譚仔係利多於弊？？","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T16:07:18.000Z","uid":10338,"like":107,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"954136c662a79a41bc5c0a527f6c6bae77423a09","tid":2032364,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"丸龜作為日本一間咁大既機構<br />\n無話行咩專制手段<br />\n無話會派d日本人嚟每間譚仔分店監督d姐姐<br />\n而且對於譚仔 係比佢哋高度自治<br />\n以三哥為例 最近推廣既活動新食物<br />\n唔會限死一定係關於總公司既日本<br />\n丸龜賣佢既烏冬 譚仔賣佢既米線<br />\n河水不犯井水<br />\n唔會無啦啦要譚仔用日文餐牌 食日本烏冬<br />\n呢d譚仔文化 唔會隨便摧毀<br />\n日本人真心好尾機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db99c13da1f225b2e6231e3590cc269bb1e01b8","tid":2032364,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"高度自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9bc5ae2910f167ecf19fd4be53ed0b3bd8d36d","tid":2032364,"uid":227262,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:34:12.000Z","msg":"湯底唔同左味，黎貨cheap左，仲加埋價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420f771b9714e060da73f011070ddcf55faa3105","tid":2032364,"uid":3987,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"D米線好似食緊膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cb4ba75ff7297ac624db794722c24e27b862a3","tid":2032364,"uid":2757,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"睇annual report話佢centralize 咗譚仔同三哥backend個食物工場，所以真係利多於弊"},{"pid":"7c09ed2053e9ee4bf8a8c1917573020748dcb696","tid":2032364,"uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf9bc5ae2910f167ecf19fd4be53ed0b3bd8d36d","tid":2032364,"uid":227262,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020